---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services — Meridian" description="Clear deliverables, custom strategy. Choose the level of SEO coverage that fits your business — Foundation, Growth, or Authority.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-dark to-dark-card pt-32 pb-20 md:pb-28">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-hero-text leading-[1.05] tracking-tight max-w-4xl">
        Clear deliverables.<br />Custom strategy.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-body-muted max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        You know exactly what you're getting every week. The thinking behind it is built for you.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tiers -->
  <section class="bg-white py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 space-y-20">

      <!-- Foundation -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-dark">Foundation</h2>
        <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-accent mt-2">$750<span class="text-lg font-normal text-light-text">/mo</span></p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-light-text">Best for: businesses that create their own content but need professional technical oversight</p>
        <div class="mt-8 space-y-4">
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">Daily GSC + rank tracking pull (up to 20 keywords)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">Live page metadata audit (title tag, meta description, H1, canonical, indexability)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">Schema markup audit — JSON-LD detection and validation (FAQPage, Organization, Product)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">Core Web Vitals monitoring via PageSpeed Insights API (LCP, CLS, FID daily)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">CTR analysis — queries with high impressions and low click-through flagged and prioritized</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">Technical issues ranked by impact — critical, warning, and informational</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">Weekly performance report with WoW trends</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">Monthly strategy review</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="border-gray-200" />

      <!-- Growth -->
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-dark">Growth</h2>
          <span class="bg-accent text-white text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Most Popular</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-accent mt-2">$1,500<span class="text-lg font-normal text-light-text">/mo</span></p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-light-text">Best for: businesses ready to scale organic content production</p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-light-text">Everything in Foundation, plus:</p>
        <div class="mt-6 space-y-4">
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">2 SEO content drafts per week (blog posts, landing pages, or optimizations)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">Weekly content intelligence brief (trending topics from your industry)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">Copy-paste technical fixes delivered — exact title tags, meta descriptions, and schema code (JSON-LD) ready to implement with no editing required</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">Post-fix monitoring — every technical fix watched for 30 days to confirm GSC movement before closing</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">Draft status tracking — nothing gets recreated, nothing gets lost</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">Friday client-ready email draft (% changes, no explanation required)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">Up to 30 keywords tracked</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">Weekly link prospecting (qualified prospects with ready-to-send outreach emails)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">Conversion decay monitoring — alerts when organic CVR drops on key pages</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">Content ROI tracking — 30/60/90-day performance milestones on published content</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">Action log — every change documented, connected to what moved in GSC</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="border-gray-200" />

      <!-- Authority -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-dark">Authority</h2>
        <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-accent mt-2">$2,500<span class="text-lg font-normal text-light-text">/mo</span></p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-light-text">Best for: competitive markets where content velocity and strategic depth matter</p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-light-text">Everything in Growth, plus:</p>
        <div class="mt-6 space-y-4">
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">Competitor gap analysis</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">Monthly strategy deck (MoM analysis, competitive signals, next-month priorities)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">Content brief reviews and edits</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">Unlimited keyword tracking</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">Priority turnaround</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">Optional publish-on-behalf — we can publish directly to your CMS so nothing sits in a draft queue</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">Backlink monitoring (link gains, losses, and domain authority changes)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">SERP feature tracking (featured snippets, PAA, knowledge panels)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3 items-start">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
            <p class="text-dark">GA4 organic funnel analysis (impression → click → session → conversion)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Platform Note -->
  <section class="bg-white pb-0 pt-0">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 pb-16">
      <div class="bg-hero-text border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 text-light-text leading-relaxed">
        Every capability on this page is a built feature maintained in our platform — not a manual process recreated each month. See what's live and what's coming on our <a href="/roadmap" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover font-medium transition-colors">feature roadmap &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Automation transparency -->
  <section class="bg-hero-text py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-[44px] font-semibold text-dark leading-tight">What's automated. What's human.</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-light-text text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">Most agencies don't publish this. We do. The automation is what makes the economics work — and what makes the work consistent.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

        <!-- Foundation -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-1">Foundation</h3>
          <p class="text-accent font-bold text-lg mb-6">$750/mo</p>
          <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-light-text uppercase tracking-widest">Runs automatically</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-light-text">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5">⚙</span>Daily GSC + rank pull</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5">⚙</span>Live page fetch — title, meta, H1, canonical, schema</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5">⚙</span>Schema validation (JSON-LD extracted from live HTML)</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5">⚙</span>Core Web Vitals via PageSpeed API</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5">⚙</span>CTR opportunity detection</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5">⚙</span>Weekly HTML report</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="border-t border-gray-100 pt-6 space-y-2">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-light-text uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Human time</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-light-text">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-dark font-medium">~20 min/week</span></li>
              <li class="text-xs">Review findings, flag issues to you</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2 mt-2"><span class="text-dark font-medium">30 min/month</span></li>
              <li class="text-xs">Strategy review call</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Growth -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border-2 border-accent relative">
          <div class="absolute -top-3 left-8">
            <span class="bg-accent text-white text-xs font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Most Popular</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-1">Growth</h3>
          <p class="text-accent font-bold text-lg mb-6">$1,500/mo</p>
          <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-light-text uppercase tracking-widest">Runs automatically</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-light-text">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5">⚙</span>Everything in Foundation</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5">⚙</span>Technical fix generation — copy-paste title tags, meta, schema</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5">⚙</span>30-day post-fix monitoring</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5">⚙</span>Weekly content intelligence pull</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5">⚙</span>2 content drafts per week</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5">⚙</span>Link prospects + outreach emails</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5">⚙</span>Conversion decay monitoring</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5">⚙</span>Friday client email draft</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="border-t border-gray-100 pt-6">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-light-text uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Human time</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-light-text">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-dark font-medium">~2 hrs/week</span></li>
              <li class="text-xs">Draft review, publishing, link prospect review, client email send</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Authority -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-1">Authority</h3>
          <p class="text-accent font-bold text-lg mb-6">$2,500/mo</p>
          <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-light-text uppercase tracking-widest">Runs automatically</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-light-text">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5">⚙</span>Everything in Growth</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5">⚙</span>Monthly strategy deck</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5">⚙</span>Backlink monitoring</li>
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5">⚙</span>SERP feature detection</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="border-t border-gray-100 pt-6">
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-light-text uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Human time</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-light-text">
              <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-dark font-medium">~3.5 hrs/week</span></li>
              <li class="text-xs">Everything in Growth, plus direct CMS publishing and monthly strategy session</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
      <p class="text-center text-sm text-light-text mt-10">The automation handles the volume. The human time handles the judgment. That's the model.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="bg-hero-text py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-[44px] font-semibold text-dark leading-tight mb-12">Frequently asked questions</h2>
      <div class="space-y-10">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-dark mb-2">Do I publish the content myself?</h3>
          <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">Yes. You get publish-ready drafts with exact WP instructions. We don't need site access.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-dark mb-2">How do you learn my brand voice?</h3>
          <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">We build a brand voice document for your business before we touch any content.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-dark mb-2">What if I already have an SEO agency?</h3>
          <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">We can audit what's been done and either complement it or replace it. We'll be honest about what we find.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-dark mb-2">How fast can we start?</h3>
          <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">Usually within one week of kickoff.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-dark mb-2">How do I know it's actually working?</h3>
          <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">Every action we take is logged with a timestamp and connected to what moved in GSC afterward. You get a client dashboard showing rankings, traffic trends, content pipeline, and a running log of everything we've done. We don't ask you to take our word for it.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-dark mb-2">What happens if rankings drop?</h3>
          <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">We catch it before you do — conversion decay monitoring and rank tracking fire daily. When something drops, you'll know why (algorithm update, new competitor content, technical regression) and you'll get a specific fix, not a vague explanation.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-dark mb-2">Is this month-to-month or a contract?</h3>
          <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">Month-to-month. SEO takes time to compound, but we'd rather earn the renewal than lock you in. Most clients stay because the data shows it working, not because they have to.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-dark mb-2">How is this different from hiring an in-house SEO?</h3>
          <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">A mid-level in-house SEO costs $70-90k/year plus benefits — and they still can't run daily automated audits, generate content intelligence, and produce link prospects simultaneously. The platform does the volume work. You get the output of a full team at a fraction of the cost.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-dark mb-2">What do you need from me to get started?</h3>
          <p class="text-light-text leading-relaxed">GSC access, GA4 read access, a short brand voice doc (or 30 minutes on a call to build one), and your top 5 competitor domains. That's it. The system handles the rest from day one.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-dark to-dark-card py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-[44px] font-semibold text-hero-text leading-tight">Not sure which tier fits?</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-body-muted text-lg">Tell us about your business and we'll recommend the right level of coverage.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="mt-10 inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-accent hover:bg-accent-hover text-white font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors">
        Let's talk
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
